(3, 'Final Fantasy 7', 2, 'Final_Fantasy_VII_Box_Art.jpg', '<p><i style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\"><b>Final Fantasy VII</b></i><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;(<span title=\"Jepang-language text\"><span lang=\"ja\">ファイナルファンタジーVII</span></span>,&nbsp;<span title=\"Hepburn transliteration\"><i lang=\"ja-Latn\">Fainaru Fantajī Sebun</i></span>)</span><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;adalah sebuah&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Permainan_peran_konsol\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Permainan peran konsol\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">permainan peran konsol</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;yang dirilis oleh&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Square_Co.,_Ltd.\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Square Co., Ltd.\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">Square Co., Ltd.</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;(sekarang&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Square_Enix\" title=\"Square Enix\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">Square Enix</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">) pada tahun 1997 dan disutradarai oleh&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Yoshinori_Kitase&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Yoshinori Kitase (halaman belum tersedia)\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">Yoshinori Kitase</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">. Ia adalah permainan pertama dalam seri&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Final_Fantasy\" title=\"Final Fantasy\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">Final Fantasy</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;yang diproduksi untuk&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Konsol_permainan\" title=\"Konsol permainan\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">konsol permainan</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/PlayStation\" title=\"PlayStation\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">Sony PlayStation</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;dan merupakan permainan pertama dalam seri ini yang diadaptasi untuk dapat dimainkan di&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Komputer_pribadi\" title=\"Komputer pribadi\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">komputer pribadi</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;berbasis&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Windows\" title=\"Microsoft Windows\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">Microsoft Windows</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">, dan permainan pertama sejak&nbsp;</span><i style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Final_Fantasy\" title=\"Final Fantasy\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Final Fantasy</a></i><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/NES\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"NES\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">NES</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;yang dirilis dengan judul yang sama baik untuk&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jepang\" title=\"Jepang\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">Jepang</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">&nbsp;dan&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amerika_Utara\" title=\"Amerika Utara\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">Amerika Utara</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">. Selain itu, ini adalah seri Final Fantasy pertama yang menggunakan&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/CGI\" class=\"mw-disambig\" title=\"CGI\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif;\">CGI</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">, dengan karakter-karakter yang dirender penuh dan latar belakang yang diprarender</span><br></p>'),
(6, 'Final Fantasy 15', 2, '91IQSCL7wtL__AC_UF1000,1000_QL80_.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 1em; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\"><i><b>Final Fantasy XV</b></i>&nbsp;(<span title=\"Jepang-language text\"><span lang=\"ja\">ファイナルファンタジーXV</span></span>,&nbsp;<span title=\"Hepburn transliteration\"><i lang=\"ja-Latn\">Fainaru Fantajī FifutĪn</i></span>)&nbsp;adalah sebuah&nbsp;<a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Permainan_video\" title=\"Permainan video\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">permainan video</a>&nbsp;untuk&nbsp;<a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/PlayStation_4\" title=\"PlayStation 4\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">PlayStation 4</a>&nbsp;dan&nbsp;<a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Xbox_One\" title=\"Xbox One\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Xbox One</a>&nbsp;yang tergabung dalam kumpulan&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Fabula_Nova_Crystallis:_Final_Fantasy&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Fabula Nova Crystallis: Final Fantasy (halaman belum tersedia)\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Fabula Nova Crystallis: Final Fantasy</a></i>.<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://www.siliconera.com/2006/05/25/more-final-fantasy-xiii-and-final-fantasy-vii-spinoffs-in-the-works/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: url(&quot;/w/skins/Vector/resources/skins.vector.styles/images/link-external-small-ltr-progressive.svg?fb64d&quot;) right center / 0.857em no-repeat; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding-right: 1em;\">[1]</a>&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20100418161025/http://www.siliconera.com/2006/05/25/more-final-fantasy-xiii-and-final-fantasy-vii-spinoffs-in-the-works/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: url(&quot;/w/skins/Vector/resources/skins.vector.styles/images/link-external-small-ltr-progressive.svg?fb64d&quot;) right center / 0.857em no-repeat; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding-right: 1em;\">Diarsipkan</a>&nbsp;2010-04-18 di&nbsp;<a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\" title=\"Wayback Machine\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Wayback Machine</a>. Terungkap pertama kali dalam&nbsp;<a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electronic_Entertainment_Expo\" title=\"Electronic Entertainment Expo\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">E3</a>&nbsp;2006 dengan nama&nbsp;<i><b>Final Fantasy Versus XIII</b></i>&nbsp;(<span title=\"Jepang-language text\"><span lang=\"ja\">ファイナルファンタジーヴェルサスXIII</span></span>,&nbsp;<span title=\"Hepburn transliteration\"><i lang=\"ja-Latn\">Fainaru Fantajī Verusasu Sātīn</i></span>)&nbsp;bersama-sama&nbsp;<a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Final_Fantasy_XIII\" title=\"Final Fantasy XIII\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Final Fantasy XIII</a>&nbsp;dan&nbsp;<a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Final_Fantasy_Type-0\" title=\"Final Fantasy Type-0\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Final Fantasy Type-0</a>, permainan ini akan memadu genre action RPG dengan third-person shooter<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 12.8px;\"><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Final_Fantasy_XV#cite_note-1\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">[1]</a></sup>&nbsp;dan mempunyai alur cerita yang dideskripsikan sebagai yang paling \"tergelap\" dalam sejarah Seri Final Fantasy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-level_magazine_2-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 12.8px;\"><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Final_Fantasy_XV#cite_note-level_magazine-2\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">[2]</a></sup>&nbsp;Dengan alur cerita, karakter, dan desain berbeda, permainan ini hanya dihubungkan bersama permainan lain dalam seri&nbsp;<i>Fabula Nova Crystallis: Final Fantasy</i>&nbsp;dengan mitos dan temanya, yaitu kristal.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 12.8px;\"><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Final_Fantasy_XV#cite_note-3\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">[3]</a></sup>&nbsp;Permainan ini akan dikembangkan oleh tim yang juga melahirkan seri permainan&nbsp;<i><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kingdom_Hearts\" title=\"Kingdom Hearts\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Kingdom Hearts</a></i>&nbsp;yang terkenal. Proyek ini akan dipimpin oleh&nbsp;<a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tetsuya_Nomura\" title=\"Tetsuya Nomura\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Tetsuya Nomura</a>.<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://na.square-enix.com/e306/titles/fabula/versus/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: url(&quot;/w/skins/Vector/resources/skins.vector.styles/images/link-external-small-ltr-progressive.svg?fb64d&quot;) right center / 0.857em no-repeat; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding-right: 1em;\">[2]</a>&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20090302121828/http://na.square-enix.com/e306/titles/fabula/versus/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: url(&quot;/w/skins/Vector/resources/skins.vector.styles/images/link-external-small-ltr-progressive.svg?fb64d&quot;) right center / 0.857em no-repeat; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding-right: 1em;\">Diarsipkan</a>&nbsp;2009-03-02 di&nbsp;<a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\" title=\"Wayback Machine\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Wayback Machine</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 1em; color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\">Semenjak terungkap pada E3 2006, informasi untuk permainan ini sangat jarang dan bentuk permainanpun baru diperlihatkan pada awal 2010. Setelah beberapa kali diisukan batal, permainan ini diungkap kembali dengan nama&nbsp;<i>Final Fantasy XV</i>&nbsp;dan konsolnya dialokasikan menjadi PlayStation 4 dan Xbox One pada E3 2013 .<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 12.8px;\"><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Final_Fantasy_XV#cite_note-4\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">[4]</a></sup></p>'),
